90后民警怒斥“口罩骗子”，获全网点赞。
90 after the police angrily rebuke "mask cheater", got the entire network praise.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 朱奕奕Play近日，一段民警怒斥“口罩骗子”的视频以4.3亿次的播放量刷爆网络。
Ju Yi Play, a journalist in Pai Pai, China, recently slammed a video of a "mask cheater" with 430 million broadcasts to blow up the network.
视频来源：上海闵行公安分局 剪辑：曾怡文(00:49)近日，一段民警怒斥“口罩骗子”的视频以4.3亿次的播放量刷爆网络。
Video Source: Min Hang Public Security Bureau Editing: Zeng Yi-wen (00: 49) A video of police raging at "mask cheaters" has blown up the network with 430 million broadcasts.
一夜间，超1500万网友点赞转评，纷纷为这位抗疫“硬核”民警打call。
One night, more than 15 million netizens praised the comments, for the plague "hard core" of the police hit call.
这名90后民警名叫戴佳伟，“走红”后依旧埋头办案，用一周连破三案的速度，刷新了个人记录。
The 90-year-old police officer named Dai Jiawei, "after the" red "still buried in the case, with a week of breaking the speed of three cases, a new record.
审讯现场。
Interrogation scene.
本文图片均由受访者 提供怒斥“口罩骗子”2月10日，虹桥龙柏派出所接到“男子诈骗购买口罩捐赠疫区的爱心人士16万元”报警，立即启动涉疫情诈骗线索快速落查机制。
Hong Qiao Long Pak Police Station received a warning of 160,000 yuan (US $160,000) from a man who had defrauded people to buy masks in areas affected by the epidemic.
原本轮班暂休的戴佳伟主动要求担负案件侦破任务，连夜彻查被害人微信聊天记录理清案情，第二天一早又一口气跑遍上海多家商场，戴佳伟迅速查明转账资金的流向，第一时间固定了嫌疑人骗取钱财挥霍一空的证据。
When Dai Jiawei, who had been on shift, volunteered to take on the task of investigating the case, conducting a night-long search through the victim's microphone records and scurrying through the Shanghai shopping malls the next morning, Mr. Dai quickly identified where the money was being transferred, first fixing the evidence that the suspect had stolen all his money.
下午，他和同事们已在嫌疑人住处开始了守候伏击，直到晚上10点人赃俱获，此时距离案件接报刚好24小时。
In the afternoon, he and his colleagues began a waiting ambush at the suspect's house until 10 p.m., just 24 hours before the case was reported.
在随后的审讯中，嫌疑人百般抵赖狡辩，一开始审讯的过程中，犯罪嫌疑人说自己要联系美国大使馆，“我要脱离中国国籍”。
At the trial that followed, the suspect denied all doubts. At the beginning of the trial, the suspect said he wanted to contact the US embassy.
明明是上海普陀人，却连自己是中国人都不承认。
Obviously Shanghai Putuo people, but even their own people do not recognize the Chinese.
面对犯罪嫌疑人一再狡辩，再考虑到疫情期间被害人购入口罩还是为了捐赠疫区，所支付的16万元订金却被其用于奢侈消费挥霍一空，戴佳伟终于难忍身为人民警察的“怒火”。
In the face of persistent debate over whether the victims bought masks or donated infected areas during the outbreak, the deposit of 160,000 yuan was used up for lavish spending.
“你还是中国人伐，你已经不要脸到这种程度了。
"You're still Chinese. You don't have the decency to do that.
”戴佳伟在审讯中开启“硬核模式”赢得网友一片好评。
"Dai Jiawei opened the" hard core mode "in the trial to win acclaim from netizens.
说起突然“走红”的经历，戴佳伟觉得主要是引起了不少网友的同感，但这样的获得感比不上破案，还是破案更有成就感。
Speaking of the sudden "popular" experience, Dai Jiawei felt that the main cause of many netizens feel the same, but such a sense of achievement than solved the case, or more sense of accomplishment.
不少抖音小姐姐也纷纷评论表示“小哥哥好帅，想嫁”，同事们纷纷截图给戴佳伟看了这些评论，他只能遗憾地表示“大家都没有这个机会了，我老婆让我当心点儿”。
Many of his younger sisters also commented that "the younger brother is so handsome, want to marry", colleagues have been shown these comments, he can only regret that "no one has this opportunity, my wife let me be careful.
戴佳伟和同事审讯犯罪嫌疑人。
David and his colleagues interrogate the suspects.
3小时找回被盗快递疫情期间一波未平一波又起，戴佳伟又投入了涉疫案件的侦破以及重点地区人员返沪排摸工作中去。
The three-hour recovery of stolen express delivery during the wave after wave, Dai Jiawei is also involved in the detection of cases of epidemic and key area personnel back to work.
对警察来说，是案件都要破。
For the police, every case has to be solved.
一部电动车、一部手机，虽然案值不大，却实实在在关系到老百姓的切身利益。
An electric car, a mobile phone, although the value of the case is not large, but the real interests of the people concerned.
比如，疫情期间，很多快递包裹被堆放在小区门外，这也让不法分子有了可乘之机。
During the outbreak, for example, many express parcels were stacked outside the compound, giving lawbreakers an opportunity to do so.
几天前，虹桥某小区居民网购了两只长脚蟹，配送小哥将蟹存放在小区简易快递柜上，后来却不翼而飞。
A few days ago, Hong Qiao residents bought a network of two long-legged crabs, the distribution of small brothers will be stored in the community on the simple express box, but later disappeared.
民警经过侦查发现，是被同小区的一位居民“顺”走了。
After investigating the police found that is the same community of a resident "Shun" walked.
“那天配送小哥来报案，投递的价值500余元的货物不见了。
"That day the delivery of younger brother to report, the delivery of more than 500 yuan of goods missing.
他很焦急，对我说，可能自己要赔偿。
He was anxious and told me that he might have to pay for it himself.
他担心案子太小不会被重视。
He feared that the case was too small to be taken seriously.
”戴佳伟回忆说，“我就对他说，你放心，我们一定会全力追查下去。
'I told him, 'You can rest assured that we will pursue it with all our might,' he recalls.
”“盒马的外包装有明显的logo，里面又是长脚蟹，辨识度很高，不太可能拿错。
"The box horse has a distinctive logo on the outside and a long-legged crab inside, and is highly recognizable and unlikely to be mistaken.
视频中这个人在取了自己的包裹后，还打开了盒马的包装看了一下，所以我推断并不是误拿。
In the video, the man unpacks a box of horses and looks at them, so I infer it wasn't taken by mistake.
”戴佳伟根据一个细节说出了自己的初步想法。
"Mr. De Gawei gave his first thoughts on a detail.
监控中嫌疑人提着蟹在小区内绕了一大圈才回的家，反常行为也更加印证了他的推断。
The abnormal behavior of the suspect, who returned home after a large circle around the area with a crab, reinforced his inference.
案情虽不复杂，侦破却没有那么顺利，疫情尚未退去，人们外出都戴着口罩，这对侦查工作造成了一定困难。
Although the case is not complex, but the detection is not so smooth, the epidemic has not receded, people wear masks outside, which caused some difficulties for the investigation.
在前期侦查过程中，戴佳伟和同事观察到嫌疑人原本是去取自己买的菜这一细节，抓住线索按迹循踪，最终成功锁定了这位“顺手牵羊”的居民，这位居民原本只是通过盒马订购了鸡毛菜，将长脚蟹带回家后获悉已经有居民报警，慌忙中还将其中一只送给了邻居掩盖此事。
In the early stages of the investigation, Dai and his colleagues observed that the suspect had originally gone to fetch the food he had bought, and tracked down the trail of a man who had ordered chicken feathers from a box-horse and brought the crab home to the police, who gave one to a neighbor to cover up the incident.
最终戴佳伟成功追回被盗长脚蟹，此时离报案仅仅3小时。
He was eventually able to recover the stolen puppy, only three hours before the case was reported.
“疫情期间快递都会堆放在小区门口。
"couriers will be stacked in front of the neighborhood during the outbreak.
”戴佳伟担心此类的行为会蔓延，因而不能放过任何一件“所谓的小事”，对社会面管控起到警示作用。
Dai worries that such behaviour will spread, leaving no "little thing" to go unnoticed, as a warning to social control.
“侦办案件就像解题，一定要细致”1994年出生，今年26岁，戴佳伟已是分局最年轻的反诈组长。
"Investigating a case is like solving a problem. Be careful." Born in 1994, at the age of 26, he is already the youngest anti-fraud chief in the police station.
毕业于辽宁工程技术大学工业设计专业，在公务员招考中，戴佳伟同时收到了公安和飞行员发来的“offer”，由于警察培训在前，戴佳伟“随机”加入了公安“大军”，走上了“打怪”之路。
Graduated from Liaoning University of Engineering and Technology in industrial design major, in the civil service recruitment examination, Dai Jiawei received public security and pilots sent "offer," because police training in the front, Dajiawei "random" joined the "army" of public security, embarked on the "hit strange.
2019年3月，虹桥派出所接报一起“创业女孩”以发红包为名实施网络诈骗的案件。
In March 2019, Hongqiao police station received a report of a "startup girl" in the name of red envelopes committed online fraud cases.
戴佳伟顶住压力，带着仅有的2条派出所接报线索，只身前往广州摸排蹲守，竟从茫茫人海中抓获了该案第一个嫌疑人，并以此为突破口，深挖出了背后隐藏着的诈骗团伙。
Dai Jiawei braved the pressure and took the only two police stations to receive the clues, only to squat in Guangzhou, but from the vast sea of people captured the first suspect in the case, and as a breakthrough, dug deep behind the hidden racket.
随后，戴佳伟又查明了该团伙的组织分工，并把全套线索提供给了分局刑侦支队。
He then identified the organizational division of the group and provided the full set of leads to the criminal investigation division of the substation.
最终，分局出动百名警力赴广州一举捣毁该诈骗团伙，抓获涉案嫌疑人40名，涉案金额逾80万元，找到被害人200余名。
In the end, the police sent 100 police officers to Guangzhou to dismantle the gang, arrested 40 suspects, involving more than 800,000 yuan, and found more than 200 victims.
一人牵出一百人犯罪团伙，戴佳伟一战成名。
One man led a gang of 100 men, and Dai Jiawei became famous.
2019年底，分局刑侦支队成立专业反诈队，在全分局抽调精干警力参与重大诈骗案件侦破，戴佳伟担任其中一个办案小组的组长。
At the end of 2019, a professional anti-fraud team was set up in the criminal investigation branch of the sub-station.
“侦办案件就像解题，一定要细致。
"Investigating a case is like solving a problem.
”戴佳伟说破案是一种习得技能和传承，2019年戴佳伟被抽掉至闵行分局反诈中心，“队里的前辈不遗余力地把经验和方法都教给了我。
"Dai Jiawei said detection was a learned skill and inheritance. In 2019, he was taken to Min Hang Sub-station Anti-Fraud Center." The senior members of the team spared no effort to teach me their experiences and methods.
”在电信诈骗类犯罪打击中，戴佳伟也遭遇了追赃难的挫折，至今只成功实现过两次追赃，“我能做的就是负责到底，抓获犯罪嫌疑人不能意味着结案。
In the fight against telecoms fraud, he has suffered a setback that has so far only succeeded in recovering the booty twice: "All I can do is see to it that the arrest of the suspect does not mean closing the case.
”一年出差15次；梳理分析过的话单、资金流水数条目以十万计，案卷资料可以铺满2个篮球场；牵头破获电信网络诈骗案近30起，带破案件400余起；抓获犯罪嫌疑人近200人，这是90后硬核民警戴佳伟在交出的一份答卷。
About 30 cases of fraud and more than 400 cases of Internet fraud have been uncovered, and nearly 200 suspects have been arrested, a questionnaire handed over by Dai Jiawei, the 90-year-old hard-core police officer.
